      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the Navier-Stokes solver; observed order within 10% of formal order.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was performed on canonical pipe flow and rotating-disk configurations. Observed spatial order of accuracy was 1.92 (formal: 2.0), within the 10% tolerance. Temporal discretization verified separately on a pulsatile flow benchmark. Code verification confirms correct implementation of the discretization scheme under nominal conditions. No verification was performed for edge-case numerical inputs that could trigger denormal floating-point arithmetic in the pressure-velocity coupling algorithm."
