      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented with calibrated instrumentation. Flow rate uncertainty ±0.05 L/min, speed uncertainty ±10 RPM, fluid viscosity matched to within 2% using glycerol-water solution at 37°C. Boundary condition mapping from experimental to simulation domain is traceable. All five operating points were reproduced in simulation with nominal solver performance."
