      "rationale": "Relative errors ranged from 3.2% to 8.7% across the five flow-speed combinations, all within the 15% acceptance criterion. Comparison performed using the same NIH formula in both experimental data reduction and post-processing script. Output comparison was conducted exclusively under nominal operating conditions; no comparison was made for conditions where the solver might produce anomalous outputs due to software faults."
